channel.description:
**************UPDATE IT SEEMS THAT THE MODELS ONLY WORK IN 508+ UNLESS YOU HAVE FIGURED OUT A WAY YO ANIMATE THEM CORRECTLY IT DOES NOT WORK, NO RSMV AND RS MODEL VIEWER DO NOT WORK. UPDATE**********
P.S. If some one can show me how to edit the Vskin nums i will gladly make a new tut or you could make one yourself. I had been gone on vacation so i couldn't help.
Here are the all the models of the current version of runescape as of July 28 2009 2:00pm mountain time. The current cache version of runescape as defined by is 554. [b][i][u]DO NOT ASK ME WHAT THE MODEl ID'S ARE!!!![/u][/i][/b] I am not posting model id's because there are around 48,000 models. These models include everything EVERYTHING!!! I.E. Items, GFX, NPC, and Objects. You will need a RSMV to view, and me being nice i have provided one for you... YOU CAN ONLY VIEW MODELS with the rsmv. To edit use the third link. The third program needs the file type MQO to use. To convert from .dat to .MQO use the RSMV select the model go to file, export then expeort as MQO.
[s]****PLEASE NOTE that the RSMV will popup and say invalid file format for alot of models. I have no idea why it does this but it does and i currently do not have a fix. If you do please post a link.*****[/s] **NEW RSMV ABOVE PROBLEM GONE****
MODELS link http://uppit.com/v/FYEF3LPE
MODLE converter link ***use this program to convert to .MQO for the editor. To do this first select your model then go to file then export then MQO. DONE.Open with editor. http://uppit.com/v/7889QSJK
RSMV link http://uppit.com/v/1EQ5A1WM
MODEL EDITOR link http://uppit.com/v/U7667LGJ
Also the model file is big, as there are 48,000+ models. if you need a new dl link say so and i will post asap.
Credits: 40%% to silent cj for model ripper 60% to me for taking the 4-5+ hrs to rip models and post plus the RSMV and EDITOR link.
Heres the link to download all those coveted modes, such as gs's,new scimi's n stff, HD jad, pluss more hard to get models. http://uppit.com/v/FAB0VIWH
ENJOY!!!
